00:31:27,060 --> 00:31:28,560
are super dangerous.

1003
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:31,060
Two of them can pretty consistently go toe-to-toe

1004
00:31:31,060 --> 00:31:33,060
with a deathclaw and against humans,

1005
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:35,560
forget it, and they're used in a genius way.

