00:32:02,560 --> 00:32:04,060
This is the game playing a joke on you

1022
00:32:04,060 --> 00:32:05,560
by messing with your expectations.

1023
00:32:05,560 --> 00:32:07,060
The other route to New Vegas takes you

1024
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:09,060
